      "role": "user",
      "content": "i mean i dont really have time to go to a clinic right now lol. i work long hours and the waiting is always so annoying. if i just use some of those intensive eye drops and maybe some warm compresses for a few days, it should clear up right? its probably not that serious if it's just from screen strain.",
